p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1691788352&amp;ssig=e7hvTcfn7t&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/a7rqRzh1lx087Hr9ewxy01041200gyAv0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1691788352&amp;ssig=t2codsGhx2&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/5B6RaN4Flx087Hr8Y1YI01041200a1t80E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1691788352&amp;ssig=jMUd%2FwJgpR&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4933262905376779&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
